      • value

        public java.lang.String value(TimeStamp.TIMESTAMP_ATTRIBUTE selector)
        Get a String representation of the attribute of this timeStamp entity selected by selector. The attribute may be a simple element of this entity as with LABOUR_SUPPLY_RESPONSE or it may depend on a calculation, as with INITTIAL_CAPITAL.
        Parameters:
        selector - the TimeStamp.TIMESTAMP_ATTRIBUTE that designates the required attribute
        Returns:
        a String representation of the designated attribute of this timeStamp entity

      • showDelta

        public java.lang.String showDelta(java.lang.String item,
                                  TimeStamp.TIMESTAMP_ATTRIBUTE selector)
        If the selected field has changed, return the difference between the current value and the former value
        Parameters:
        selector - chooses which field to evaluate
        item - the original item - returned as the result if there is no change
        Returns:
        the original item if nothing has changed, otherwise the change, as an appropriately formatted string
